com.qbyteconsulting
Class HyperOrderIF

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.qbyteconsulting.HyperOrderIF
public final class HyperOrderIF
extends java.lang.Object

This class uses the hoctsjni.dll to provide operation of HyperOrder. All code included in this project should be treated as untested prototype material, and is provided as an example of how to implement the JNI. Although the code is operational, you are not advised to use it in a live trading environment.

Native methods have been provided for all of the basic trading functions. In some cases the method functions have not been implemented in the DLL, although the interface exists.

Documentation is provided by the HyperOrder SDK.

Version:
0.9
Author:
John Coleman
